                                <p>
                                    Strictly For; Vendors, Outsiders, Insiders and Contributors Promotional Message Posting Guidelines</p>
                                <p>
                                    Please read through our guidelines and expectations before submitting an article, a promotional message, a review or a comment on our GetValue.co <strong>Affiliate Blogging Section</strong> of the site. The Vendor, Insiders and Contributors <strong>Affiliate Blogging Section</strong> posting Guidelines are divided in four categories;</p>
